    "sections": {
        "description": "<p><a href=\"https://fortguard.io\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Fortguard</a> is a state-of-the-art spam detection API for commenting systems, forums, email clients, and many other applications.</p>\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Real-time spam detection</li>\n<li>Access to state-of-the art LLMs</li>\n<li>Spam threshold</li>\n<li>Spam by location</li>\n<li>Spam by language</li>\n<li>Supports any language</li>\n<li>Spam by sentiments</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://fortguard.io/console\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"><strong>Fortguard Console</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://fortguard.io/pricing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"><strong>Pricing</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://fortguard.io/docs\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"><strong>Docs</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://fortguard.io/docs/privacy\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"><strong>Privacy Policy</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://fortguard.io/docs/terms\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"><strong>Terms of Service</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n",
        "installation": "<h4>Pre-requisits</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>You must have a <strong>Fortguard account</strong> and a <strong>Fortguard Project</strong> to use this plugin.</li>\n<li>If you do not have a account yet, <a href=\"https://fortguard.io/signup\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">sign up now</a> and create a project. </li>\n<li>If you do have a Fortguard account but no project for your WordPress site, <a href=\"https://fortguard.io/console/new\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">create a new project now</a>.</li>\n<li>Copy your Project <strong>API KEY</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In the WordPress admin panel,</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Plugins</strong> &gt; <strong>Add New</strong></li>\n<li>Type <strong>fortguard</strong> in the search box</li>\n<li>Find <strong>Fortguard Spam Protection</strong> by Hyvor</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Install Now</strong></li>\n<li>Activate the plugin</li>\n<li>Go to Fortguard plugin</li>\n<li>Add Fortguard API Key and click <strong>Save</strong>. (<em>You can find you API Key at the <a href=\"https://fortguard.io/console\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">console</a>.</em>)</li>\n<li>Configure your preferred spam detection criteria and click <strong>Change</strong>. (<em>You may change these criteria at any time.</em>)</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='do%20i%20need%20an%20api%20key%20to%20use%20this%20plugin%3F'>\nDo I need an API key to use this plugin?\n</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes. You need to sign up at <a href=\"https://fortguard.io\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FortGuard</a> to get an API key.</p>\n</p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Introduced Fortguard WordPress plugin.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
